  <section>
    <div class="wrap">
      <header>
        <h1>Massage Therapy</h1>
      </header>
      
      <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <p style="color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 16px;">
          We offer therapeutic massage services to support both mental and physical wellness. 
          Our practice has a no-tipping policy.
        </p>
        <p style="color: var(--muted);">
          For specialties and details, see <a href="/team/ruth-bucher">Ruth Bucher's</a> page.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <h3>Benefits</h3>
        <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 20px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 12px;">
          <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Pain relief and management</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Trauma recovery support</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Stress reduction</li>
          <li>Improved physical and mental wellness</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div style="margin-top: 24px;">
        <a href="/services/overview" class="btn tertiary">‚Üê Back to Services</a>
